= ec2nodefinder =

This is a rebundling from the Dukes of Erl's ec2nodefinder : http://dukesoferl.blogspot.com/2008/02/automatic-node-discovery.html

= License =
New BSD license (http://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.php) as the original code is.

= Building =

./rebar compile
./rebar install

= Running = 

You need to set the access and secret values for AWS authentication. 
OR if you have the AMAZON_ACCESS_KEY_ID and AMAZON_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY environment variables set, ec2nodefinder will automatically pick them up.

